"Gut Health\\\",\\n      \\\"score\\\": 68\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\\n              Axis Scores: {\\n  \\\"1\\\": {\\n    \\\"axisName\\\": \\\"Inflammation\\\",\\n    \\\"score\\\": 75\\n  },\\n  \\\"3\\\": {\\n    \\\"axisName\\\": \\\"Metabolic\\\",\\n    \\\"score\\\": 80\\n  },\\n  \\\"9\\\": {\\n    \\\"axisName\\\": \\\"Gut Health\\\",\\n    \\\"score\\\": 68\\n  }\\n}\\n              Format: Markdown content.\\n            \"}]}],\"config\":{},\"output\":{\"schema\":{\"def\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"shape\":{\"chapterNumber\":{\"def\":{\"type\":\"number\",\"checks\":[]},\"type\":\"number\",\"minValue\":null,\"maxValue\":null,\"isInt\":false,\"isFinite\":true,\"format\":null},\"title\":{\"def\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"type\":\"string\",\"format\":null,\"minLength\":null,\"maxLength\":null},\"content\":{\"def\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"type\":\"string\",\"format\":null,\"minLength\":null,\"maxLength\":null},\"summary\":{\"def\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"type\":\"string\",\"format\":null,\"minLength\":null,\"maxLength\":null}}},\"type\":\"object\"},\"format\":\"json\",\"jsonSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},\"use\":[]}","genkit:output":"{\"message\":{\"role\":\"model\",\"content\":[{\"text\":\"{\\\"chapter_number\\\":8,\\\"chapter_title\\\":\\\"Proteomics and Metabolomics: Systems-Level Molecular Integration\\\",\\\"patient_profile\\\":\\\"คุณจารุณี (52-year-old female, Business Owner)\\\",\\\"analysis_framework\\\":\\\"Systems Biology Clinical Intelligence Engine\\\",\\\"proteomic_findings\\\":\\\"Analysis reveals a heightened Proteomic Signature of Systemic Inflammation characterized by an elevated hs-CRP (4.5 mg/L) and a Genetic Predisposition to High TNF-alpha Expression. The Inflammation Axis Score of 75/100 correlates with an upregulated Cytokine Profile, specifically TNF-alpha and likely IL-6, which are potent drivers of the neuro-inflammatory signaling manifesting clinically as 'Brain Fog'. The elevation of ALT (42 U/L) signals a p